ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Our app uses advanced algorithms and data mining techniques to scour the internet for information on upcoming product releases. We curate and present this data in a user-friendly interface, allowing you to easily explore new products based on your preferences and interests.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: FindNewProducts covers a wide range of categories, including technology, fashion, home goods, beauty, and more. Whether you're a gadget enthusiast, a fashion-forward trendsetter, or simply someone who loves staying up-to-date with the latest innovations, our app has something for everyone.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is the app free to use?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, FindNewProducts is completely free to download and use. We believe in democratizing access to information about new products, empowering consumers to make informed decisions and stay ahead of the curve.

FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Is the app free to use?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, the app is completely free to download and use. We don't charge any subscription fees.

FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Absolutely! Our app allows you to easily share product recommendations with your friends and family through social media or messaging apps.
